				p.lead There could be many websites that exist and provide similar services that BisRing does, so why come here? BisRing provides a platform where you can find every possible real-estate interactions. We allow the users to access real-estate related Services, Rent and Sales all in one location.
				p With these three primary categories, it allows us to create various sub categories that fall under each one and market to a large variety of businesses. Under services you will find a wide variety of businesses that provide every service you can possibly think of that falls under real-estate. It ranges from plumbers, electricians, house cleaners, Real-estate Lawyers to mentors who will educate you about the real-estate field. For rent and sale, we offer categories such as housing, tools, materials, appliances, and furniture. These are just a sample of the many categories we offer, we wanted to hit every aspect of the real-estate field as much as possible and cover all grounds.
				p BisRingers can create virtual teams to access and dynamically stay up to date with professionals in the industry which eliminates outdated business contacts from business cards, mobiles and emails. If you are working on a project and require services from several businesses, you can add them to your virtual team and you have access to all of them in one location. You can create virtual teams based off locations you are working at, so you can only include businesses that work in that area.
				p All kinds of businesses related to real-estate can market themselves through our well categorized and structured platform to attain global exposure. BisRing offers unique features for the businesses to promote and develop themselves on a global scale and network with one another.
				p When a user leaves a review, we make sure our admins go through every review thoroughly to make sure they follow our guidelines. We want to make sure our ProBisRingers aren&rsquo;t being attacked by users and being falsely accused of providing terrible service and being unpleasant with clients. We take reviews very seriously as it affects the business of many users and we want to ensure everyone is satisfied by the end.
